       "functools.update_wrapper.__qualname__.__len__() == 14 — update_wrapper is a pure-Python function defined in Lib/functools.py; its __qualname__ attribute is the string 'update_wrapper' (14 chars); str.__len__() returns 14; no prior functools spec checks update_wrapper.__qualname__.__len__() via functoolsextra87; new to extra87"]
    - [lru_cache_qualname_len_eq_9,
