       "functools.lru_cache.__qualname__.__len__() == 9 — lru_cache is a pure-Python decorator defined in Lib/functools.py; its __qualname__ attribute is the string 'lru_cache' (9 chars); str.__len__() returns 9; no prior functools spec checks lru_cache.__qualname__.__len__() via functoolsextra87; new to extra87"]
    - [reduce_name_len_eq_6,
