       "functools.reduce.__name__.__len__() == 6 — reduce is a C builtin function; its __name__ attribute is the string 'reduce' (6 chars); str.__len__() returns 6; no prior functools spec checks reduce.__name__.__len__() via functoolsextra87; new to extra87"]

